gram.com/p/DXMz0n6AHmE" /><meta property="fb:app_id" content="124024574287414" /><meta property="instapp:owner_user_id" content="57256207905" /><meta name="description" content="39K likes, 1,208 comments - atelierjolieofficial on April 16, 2026: &quot;Atelier Jolie proudly presents the Tatale &#064;tataleworld Dining Series by &#064;akwasibrenyamensa.&#x2028;&#x2028;Born in Ghana and developed in London, Tatale is a contemporary Pan-African concept that tells stories through food, art and heritage.&#x2028;&#x2028;Presented weekly, &#064;akwasibrenyamensa brings a series of intimate dinners to Atelier Jolie, becoming the first-ever culinary artist to offer a dining experience within the creative hub. The series explores a program of evolving menus, inviting artists and makers including &#064;hawahassan &#064;natashapickowicz and &#064;artcomesfirst to collaborate through communal dining.

Opens Friday, April 24, 2026. Details at the link in our bio.

Photos by &#064;argenisphoto

