#AtelierJolie #Tatale #AkwasiBrenyaMensa&quot;" /><meta property="og:image" content="https://scontent.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/670290596_18003628517911906_7952751806744225460_n.jpg?stp=c288.0.864.864a_dst-jpg_e35_s640x640_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=100&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=18de74&amp;efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiQ0FST1VTRUxfSVRFTS5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=ubI6rhdw-iMQ7kNvwE74zX0&amp;_nc_oc=Adr2K_h2Aas6IBMxRlaOeSErIO5dIOISzbJTKjz1D3JZqCLcVS7i5NRW2VYyiwYljoSkOw8Cmwh7avGoTRipU4V6&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=9jHyCIIflxFndp2N3eHA4w&amp;_nc_ss=7b689&amp;oh=00_Af0SPgQQOOo97HGdhaNyz93vXlaZbWcoQsKpLZNc_ctw7Q&amp;oe=69F89D18" /><meta property="og:url" content="https://www.instagram.com/atelierjolieofficial/p/DXMz0n6AHmE/" /><meta property="og:description" content="39K likes, 1,208 comments - atelierjolieofficial on April 16, 2026: &quot;Atelier Jolie proudly presents the Tatale &#064;tataleworld Dining Series by &#064;akwasibrenyamensa.&#x2028;&#x2028;Born in Ghana and developed in London, Tatale is a contemporary Pan-African concept that tells stories through food, art and heritage.&#x2028;&#x2028;Presented weekly, &#064;akwasibrenyamensa brings a series of intimate dinners to Atelier Jolie, becoming the first-ever culinary artist to offer a dining experience within the creative hub. The series explores a program of evolving menus, inviting artists and makers including &#064;hawahassan &#064;natashapickowicz and &#064;artcomesfirst to collaborate through communal dining.

Opens Friday, April 24, 2026. Details at the link in our bio.

Photos by &#064;argenisphoto

