x2lah0s x1q0g3np xqjyukv x1qjc9v5 x1oa3qoh x1nhvcw1"><a class="x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x1ejq31n x18oe1m7 x1sy0etr xstzfhl x972fbf x10w94by x1qhh985 x14e42zd x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 x3ct3a4 xdj266r x14z9mp xat24cr x1lziwak xexx8yu xyri2b x18d9i69 x1c1uobl x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz notranslate _a6hd" href="/atelierjolieofficial/" role="link" tabindex="0" target="_blank"><div class="html-div xdj266r x14z9mp xat24cr x1lziwak xexx8yu xyri2b x18d9i69 x1c1uobl x9f619 xjbqb8w x1rg5ohu x15mokao x1ga7v0g x16uus16 xbiv7yw x1uhb9sk x1plvlek xryxfnj x1c4vz4f x2lah0s x1oa3qoh"><div class="html-div xdj266r x14z9mp xat24cr x1lziwak xexx8yu xyri2b x18d9i69 x1c1uobl x9f619 xjbqb8w x78zum5 x15mokao x1ga7v0g x16uus16 xbiv7yw x1n2onr6 x1plvlek xryxfnj x1c4vz4f x2lah0s x1q0g3np xqjyukv x6s0dn4 x1oa3qoh x1nhvcw1"><span class="_ap3a _aaco _aacw _aacx _aad7 _aade" dir="auto">atelierjolieofficial</span><div class="html-div xdj266r x14z9mp xat24cr xexx8yu xyri2b x18d9i69 x1c1uobl x9f619 xjbqb8w x1rg5ohu x15mokao x1ga7v0g x16uus16 xbiv7yw xdwrcjd x1n2onr6 x1plvlek xryxfnj x1c4vz4f x2lah0s x1oa3qoh"><svg aria-label="Verified" class="x1lliihq x1n2onr6" fill="rgb(0, 149, 246)" height="12" role="img" viewBox="0 0 40 40" width="12"><title>Verified</title><path d="M19.998 3.094 14.638 0l-2.972 5.15H5.432v6.354L0 14.64 3.094 20 0 25.359l5.432 3.137v5.905h5.975L14.638 40l5.36-3.094L25.358 40l3.232-5.6h6.162v-6.01L40 25.359 36.905 20 40 14.641l-5.248-3.03v-6.46h-6.419L25.358 0l-5.36 3.094Zm7.415 11.225 2.254 2.287-11.43 11.5-6.835-6.93 2.244-2.258 4.587 4.581 9.18-9.18Z" fill-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></div></div></div></a> <span class="x193iq5w xeuugli x1fj9vlw x13faqbe x1vvkbs xt0psk2 x1i0vuye xvs91rp xo1l8bm x1roi4f4" style="line-height:18px">Edited</span><span class="html-span xdj266r xat24cr xexx8yu xyri2b x18d9i69 x1c1uobl x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs x1rg5ohu xdwrcjd x2fvf9"><span class="x193iq5w xeuugli x1fj9vlw x13faqbe x1vvkbs xt0psk2 x1i0vuye xvs91rp xo1l8bm x1roi4f4" style="line-height:18px">•</span></span><span class="x193iq5w xeuugli x1fj9vlw x13faqbe x1vvkbs xt0psk2 x1i0vuye xvs91rp xo1l8bm x1roi4f4" style="line-height:18px"><time class="xdwrcjd" dateTime="2026-04-16T17:01:35.000Z" title="Apr 16, 2026">1w</time></span></div><span class="x193iq5w xeuugli x13faqbe x1vvkbs xt0psk2 x1i0vuye xvs91rp xo1l8bm x5n08af x126k92a" style="line-height:18px">Atelier Jolie proudly presents the Tatale <a class="x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x1ejq31n x18oe1m7 x1sy0etr xstzfhl x972fbf x10w94by x1qhh985 x14e42zd x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 x3ct3a4 xdj266r x14z9mp xat24cr x1lziwak xexx8yu xyri2b x18d9i69 x1c1uobl x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz notranslate _a6hd" href="/tataleworld/" role="link" tabindex="0">@tataleworld</a> Dining Series by <a class="x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x1ejq31n x18oe1m7 x1sy0etr xstzfhl x972fbf x10w94by x1qhh985 x14e42zd x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 x3ct3a4 xdj266r x14z9mp xat24cr x1lziwak xexx8yu xyri2b x18d9i69 x1c1uobl x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz notranslate _a6hd" href="/akwasibrenyamensa/" role="link" tabindex="0">@akwasibrenyamensa</a>.  Born in Ghana and developed in London, Tatale is a contemporary Pan-African concept that tells stories through food, art and heritage.  Presented weekly, <a class="x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x1ejq31n x18oe1m7 x1sy0etr xstzfhl x972fbf x10w94by x1qhh985 x14e42zd x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 x3ct3a4 xdj266r x14z9mp xat24cr x1lziwak xexx8yu xyri2b x18d9i69 x1c1uobl x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz notranslate _a6hd" href="/akwasibrenyamensa/" role="link" tabindex="0">@akwasibrenyamensa</a> brings a series of intimate dinners to Atelier Jolie, becoming the first-ever culinary artist to offer a dining experience within the creative hub. The series explores a program of evolving menus, inviting artists and makers including <a class="x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x1ejq31n x18oe1m7 x1sy0etr xstzfhl x972fbf x10w94by x1qhh985 x14e42zd x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 x3ct3a4 xdj266r x14z9mp xat24cr x1lziwak xexx8yu xyri2b x18d9i69 x1c1uobl x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a