e with my father—we are just trying to survive together. But you&#x27;ve been a part of our lives since I was a boy, playing &#x27;Tomb Raider&#x27; with my dad. I know life hasn&#x27;t been easy for you either, and your strength gives me hope to keep fighting for us. Thank you for being an inspiration.&quot;</span></div></div></div><div class="html-div x14z9mp xat24cr x1lziwak xexx8yu xyri2b x18d9i69 x1c1uobl x9f619 x16ye13r xjbqb8w x78zum5 x15mokao x1ga7v0g x16uus16 xbiv7yw x1xmf6yo x1uhb9sk x1plvlek xryxfnj x1c4vz4f x2lah0s x1q0g3np xqjyukv x6s0dn4 x1oa3qoh x1nhvcw1" style="--x-height:16px"><button class="_a9ze"><span class="x1lliihq x1plvlek xryxfnj x1n2onr6 xyejjpt x15dsfln x193iq5w xeuugli x1fj9vlw x13faqbe x1vvkbs x1s928wv xhkezso x1gmr53x x1cpjm7i x1fgarty x1943h6x x1i0vuye x1fhwpqd x1s688f x1roi4f4" style="--x---base-line-clamp-line-height:16px;--x-lineHeight:16px" dir="auto">Like</span></button><div class="x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x1ejq31n x18oe1m7 x1sy0etr xstzfhl x972fbf x10w94by x1qhh985 x14e42zd x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 x3ct3a4 xdj266r xat24cr x1lziwak xexx8yu xyri2b x18d9i69 x1c1uobl x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz xbmvrgn x87ps6o x1d5wrs8" role="button" tabindex="0"><span class="x1lliihq x1plvlek xryxfnj x1n2onr6 xyejjpt x15dsfln x193iq5w xeuugli x1fj9vlw x13faqbe x1vvkbs x1s928wv xhkezso x1gmr53x x1cpjm7i x1fgarty x1943h6x x1i0vuye x1fhwpqd x1s688f x1roi4f4 x1s3etm8 x676frb" style="--x---base-line-clamp-line-height:16px;--x-lineHeight:16px" dir="auto"><span class="x1lliihq x193iq5w x6ikm8r x10wlt62 xlyipyv xuxw1ft">Reply</span></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="html-div xdj266r x14z9mp xat24cr x1lziwak xexx8yu xyri2b x18d9i69 x1c1uobl x9f619 xjbqb8w x78zum5 x15mokao x1ga7v0g x16uus16 xbiv7yw x1uhb9sk x1plvlek xryxfnj x1c4vz4f x2lah0s xdt5ytf xqjyukv x1qjc9v5 x1oa3qoh x1nhvcw1"><div><div class="html-div xdj266r x14z9mp xat24cr x1lziwak xyri2b x1c1uobl x9f619 xjbqb8w x78zum5 x15mokao x1ga7v0g x16uus16 xbiv7yw xsag5q8 xz9dl7a x1uhb9