Tatale (@tataleworld) dining series by @akwasibrenyamensa arrives at @AtelierJolieOfficial Jolie on April 24.

Born in Ghana and developed in London, Tatale is a contemporary Pan-African dining concept telling stories through food, art and heritage.

Tickets are now live at the link in bio.

24th April - 10th July 2026.

